706507f-a.text:
(1)
Rockaway Ave., east side, south from Ditmas Ave. Iu the foreground, is the Rockaway Ave., Trolley Line. The 2-story building below the mast, is No. 1095 Rockaway Ave.
July 30, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same a further view south, from 1095; at the right is Ditmas Ave. In the background is the trestle of the Long Island R.R. freight
division.
July 3o, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
706507f-a.folder: Rockaway Avenue & Ditmas Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
